The application serves the purpose of verifying whether a thermometer that the cherry board is equipped with takes reliable measurements.

Every two seconds the application makes a call to a thermometer driver and asks for a measurement of temperature.

*************
REMARKS
*************
- As for now, the cherry board is equipped with a thermometer TMP431A (of address 0x4C).
- Temperature value is given in tenths of Celsius degrees.
- One should expect an outcome that is similar to:
>> Temperature in tenths of degree Celsius: 257
>> Temperature in tenths of degree Celsius: 257
>> Temperature in tenths of degree Celsius: 258
>> Temperature in tenths of degree Celsius: 257
>> ...
